{"tid":281110,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[JJ插沙求救] 上網速度同RAM問題求救","createTime":"2017-06-12T12:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T19:56:48.000Z","uid":42043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64229e192f6484892d4357fb01a93e58dcb93610","tid":281110,"uid":42043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:59:23.000Z","msg":"家下有兩個問題, 想請各位救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我而家部機本身因為只Support 10/100M上網既關係<br />\n我自已買左張1000M既LAN卡<br />\n<br />\n而家Ethernet Card顯示係1.0Gbps上網<br />\n但係speed test只能夠100Mbps內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我用另外一部Notebook就可以去到800Mbps左右<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/OknWG2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FOknWG2.png&h=d3c615da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/f036j8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Ff036j8.png&h=c5b52c94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會唔會關個底板事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外, 因為呢塊底板好似只support 8Gb RAM<br />\n會唔會有方法令佢Support 16Gb?<br />\n(例如更新firmware之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n底板: Koloe x58 (唔知咩牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n解決到既話可以幫大家免費含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7011139faef8e3f5805e232c36b8414d048379","tid":281110,"uid":56328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:01:12.000Z","msg":"你塊板<br />\nLAN<br />\nRealtek&reg; RTL8105E 10/100M<br />\n<br />\n要買過張LAN卡"},{"pid":"4e92b0232dc343fea3f5fd0eb75b712bde6ed97f","tid":281110,"uid":42043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:12:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你塊板<br />\nLAN<br />\nRealtek&reg; RTL8105E 10/100M<br />\n<br />\n要買過張LAN卡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就係岩岩買左張LAN卡<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/RBeTSa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FRBeTSa.png&h=47e6e908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個Speed係1.0Gbps (如第一個PO個張圖)<br />\n但係唔知點解Speed Test個個Download Speed唔夠1000Mbps<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f8bc9ed6974e17b46956184b383053306a918d","tid":281110,"uid":42043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:40:07.000Z","msg":"Sorry推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e523eb64088722b7ea5ca685e1b42ce103c5eb","tid":281110,"uid":18283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:56:48.000Z","msg":"你部機嘅spec?"}]}